Targeted Customer Analysis

This repository contains the code and datasets used for analyzing mall customer demographics and segmenting them into meaningful groups based on spending behavior. The project demonstrates practical skills in exploratory data analysis (EDA), clustering, visualization, and customer segmentation.


Contents

Mall_Customers.csv – Dataset used for analysis
Analysis Script (R/Python) – Code for data cleaning, EDA, clustering
Output Screenshots


Project Summary

The project performs customer segmentation using demographic and spending data.
Key steps include:
Data cleaning & preprocessing
Exploratory data analysis
Applying K-Means clustering
Visualizing customer groups
Interpreting segments for targeted marketing


Objective

To identify customer groups based on:
Annual income
Spending score
Age and gender patterns


Techniques Used

K-Means Clustering
Scatter Plots & Pairwise Visualizations
Basic statistical summaries
